name: Skara - The Blade Remains
blurb: Help Launch Skara- a struggle to survive on a dying planet filled with hand-to-hand combat and multiplayer online battle arenas.

rewards.reward: No Reward

Please only choose this tier if you are able to spend time testing, are willing to write bug reports, are willing and able to sign a non-disclosure agreement and not emplyed by or working for another company that creates games. You get invites to ALL ALPHA & BETA TESTING + ALL PREVIOUS DIGITAL & PHYSICAL REWARDS (except limited) + EXTRA OPEN BETA INVITE (5 Total) + OFFICIAL 'BETA TESTER FOR SKARA' BADGE + PHYSICAL SKARA COMIC BOOK. PART OF THE TEAM - DIGITAL & PHYSICAL ============================== Welcome to Team Skara! You will be able to talk and hang out with the Skara Team in Barcelona, Spain, share a great time with all of us and to ask or suggest anything you like about Skara. You must provide your own transportation to our office,  but we will take care of your  accommodation in a nearby hotel and all your meals with the team during your stay in Barcelona. And off course, you get ALL PREVIOUS PHYSICAL & DIGITAL REWARDS (INCLUDING LIMITED!!!) + 10 EXTRA OPEN BETA INVITES (30 Total) + 300 HONOR POINTS (700 total) + THE ALL FIVE 25 cms. FIGURES OF THE SKARA CHARACTERS.+ A GOLDEN STATUE OF YOURSELF IN THE COLISEUM our one-vs-one battle arena + be the MAIN CHARACTER of the Story Mode for the race of your choice. All the users that play the Story Mode will do with your name and your character. Isn\u00b4t exciting?
